                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "Snowball sampling rarely produces a sample that is representative of the population."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "It is challenging to find enough participants to obtain a large enough sample."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "Snowball samples can never provide quantitative data."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_4",
                  "content": "Snowball samples can never provide qualitative data."
